<item>
            <title>[SPR-9370] HttpStatusCodeException not serializable</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-9370</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;My app use an exception reporting framework that depends on the fact that all exceptions should be serializable. When org.springframework.web.client.HttpStatusCodeException is thrown in a RestTemplate method, the exception reporting framework complains that a Charset object in the HttpStatusCodeException is not serializable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="43173">SPR-9370</key>
            <summary>HttpStatusCodeException not serializable</summary>
